Interface FileUploader


  • public interface FileUploader
    Interface to allow custom handling of image and file uploads.
    See Also:
    ELJBean.setFileUploader(FileUploader)

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      FileUploadResult uploadFile(File file)
      Uploads the file and returns the String url to the file.

    • Method Detail

      • uploadFile

        FileUploadResult uploadFile(File file)
        Uploads the file and returns the String url to the file. All references to the file in the document will be updated with the string result of this method. Note: Return type changed from String to FileUploadResult in 9.1.0.283
        Parameters:
        file - A reference to the local resource that must be uploaded
        Returns:
        the URL path to the uploaded file, or null if the upload failed
